## API

### Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|------|
| `modelValue` | `number \| string` | `0` | TextValue |
| `segments` | `SegmentedSliderSegment[]` | `[]` | Description for segments. |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | `false` | Description for disabled. |
| `showLabels` | `boolean` | `true` | Description for showLabels. |
| `vertical` | `boolean` | `false` | Description for vertical. |

### SegmentedSliderSegment

| Prop | Type | Description |
|------|------|------|
| `value` | `number \| string` | OptionsValue |
| `label` | `string` | Description for label. |

### Events

| Event | Params | Description |
|------|------|------|
| `update:modelValue` | `(value: number \| string)` | ValueTextTrigger |
| `change` | `(value: number \| string)` | ValueTextTrigger |
